Aesthetics = object
  x*: Option[Scale]
  y*: Option[Scale]
  fill*: Option[Scale]
  color*: Option[Scale]
  size*: Option[Scale]
  shape*: Option[Scale]

ScaleKind = enum
  scLinearData, scTransformedData, scColor, scFillColor, scShape, scSize
PositionKind = enum
  pkIdentity = "identity", pkStack = "stack", pkDodge = "dodge", pkFill = "fill"
DiscreteKind = enum
  dcDiscrete, dcContinuous
ScaleValue = object
  case kind*: ScaleKind
  of scLinearData, scTransformedData:
      val*: Value

  of scFillColor, scColor:
      color*: Color

  of scShape:
      marker*: MarkerKind

  of scSize:
      size*: float

  
SecondaryAxis = object
  trans*: Option[FormulaNode]
  name*: string
  axKind*: AxisKind

Scale = object
  col*: string
  name*: string
  vKind*: ValueKind
  case scKind*: ScaleKind
  of scLinearData, scTransformedData:
      axKind*: AxisKind
      trans*: proc (v: Value): Value
      secondaryAxis*: Option[SecondaryAxis]

  else:
    nil
  case dcKind*: DiscreteKind
  of dcDiscrete:
      valueMap*: OrderedTable[Value, ScaleValue]
      labelSeq*: seq[Value]

  of dcContinuous:
      dataScale*: ginger.Scale
      mapData*: proc (idxs: seq[int] = @[]): seq[ScaleValue]

  
Facet = object
  columns*: seq[string]

Draw = object
  fname*: string
  width*: Option[float]
  height*: Option[float]

VegaDraw = object
  nil

GeomKind = enum
  gkPoint, gkBar, gkHistogram, gkFreqPoly, gkTile, gkLine
Geom = object
  data*: Option[DataFrame]
  style*: Option[Style]
  position*: PositionKind
  aes*: Aesthetics
  case kind*: GeomKind
  of gkHistogram, gkFreqPoly:
      numBins*: int
      binWidth*: float

  else:
      nil

  
Theme = object
  xlabel*: Option[string]
  xlabelMargin*: Option[float]
  ylabel*: Option[string]
  ylabelMargin*: Option[float]
  legendPosition*: Option[Coord]
  discreteScaleMargin*: Option[Quantity]

GgPlot[T] = object
  data*: T
  title*: string
  subtitle*: string
  aes*: Aesthetics
  numXticks*: int
  numYticks*: int
  facet*: Option[Facet]
  geoms*: seq[Geom]
  theme*: Theme
